        <paragraph>The Object Storage services (swift) work together to provide
            object storage and retrieval through a REST API.</paragraph>
        <paragraph>This chapter assumes a working setup of OpenStack following the
            <reference name="OpenStack Installation Tutorial" refuri="http://docs.openstack.org/#install-guides">OpenStack Installation Tutorial</reference><target ids="openstack-installation-tutorial" names="openstack\ installation\ tutorial" refuri="http://docs.openstack.org/#install-guides"></target>.</paragraph>
        <paragraph>Your environment must at least include the Identity service (keystone)
            prior to deploying Object Storage.</paragraph>
